      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS timing. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a preventive rod bearing service to ensure mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension remains taut with OEM-spec bushings and dampers, maintaining the original handling dynamics. The exterior retains its deep luster with no paint imperfections, while the interior features immaculate Nappa leather with zero bolster fatigue. A masterfully maintained example for the discerning collector.",
